snippet.title: Finding Nickelodeon's LOST PlayStation Game | Finding CatDog: Saving Mean Bob [LOST MEDIA]
snippet.description:
23 years ago a mysterious CatDog game was announced for the PlayStation. Despite advertisements, press previews, and an announced release date, the game vanished into thin air with no explanation, never to be seen again. This is the story of my year-long journey to unravel the mystery of CatDog: Saving Mean Bob.

You can follow me on Twitter here: https://twitter.com/saucemarlow
